Brainyfun is dedicated to providing a fun and educational experience for all users. We take your privacy seriously and will only use your personal information as described in this privacy policy.

We do not collect any personal information from users. The app does not require any login or registration. Any information entered into the app, such as answers to quizzes or puzzles, is only stored on your device and is not transmitted to us or any third parties.

We do not use any third-party analytics or advertising services in our app.

If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at danieljermaine97@gmail.com"
